autoviral design/
# mattpocock skills bundle — installed via `npx skills add mattpocock/skills`,
# symlinked into .claude/skills/. Not committed: each teammate runs `npx skills`
# locally to get the current version they prefer.
.agents/
# npx skills installer also drops symlinks into ./skills/<name> pointing at
# ../.agents/skills/<name>. Symlinks would be broken on any clone. Only the
# AutoViral skill itself (skills/autoviral/) stays committed.
skills/*
!skills/autoviral
skills-lock.json
